        </div></div></div><div class="xmobile-6 medium-3 column end"><div class="article-box"><a href="/poradniki/dla-pracodawcow/targi-pracy-100-w-punkt_pr-1688.html" class="article-thumbnail" style="background-image:url(/pressroom/poradniki/345x260/345x260_2.jpg)"><span class="article-title">
